{"id":231314187,"title":"帶自己的便當盒，老闆就多送菜","content":"之前男友帶了自己的便當盒去買便當的時候\n老闆看到非常的開心\n告訴我們他很鼓勵大家帶自己的盒子來裝\n因此多送了一樣菜\n由於是正中午就大排長龍的便當店\n為了省時間就比較少去買\n前幾天我帶著自己的便當盒去裝\n本來想說人多應該就不會送了吧？\n沒想到我買了兩份都各多送一樣菜（菜是自己挑的）\n因為怕耽誤老闆的時間\n就說要自己扣便當盒（上下層的那種）\n結果老闆還很可愛的說他想試試看😂\n\n順道一提\n老闆跟老闆娘都很親切\n便當也好吃\n所以生意才那麼好\n\n附上我的便當盒照片\nhttps://i.imgur.com/baRNKeK.jpg","excerpt":"之前男友帶了自己的便當盒去買便當的時候，老闆看到非常的開心，告訴我們他很鼓勵大家帶自己的盒子來裝，因此多送了一樣菜，由於是正中午就大排長龍的便當店，為了省時間就比較少去買，前幾天我帶著自己的便當盒去裝","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-05-18T10:44:46.360Z","updatedAt":"2019-05-18T10:44:46.360Z","commentCount":11,"likeCount":153,"tags":[],"topics":["環保"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"國立金門大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":153}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/baRNKeK.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"85359a7d-0fc2-4943-9da7-1e5b75b61b46","url":"https://i.imgur.com/baRNKeK.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/baRNKeK.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/baRNKeK.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-05-18T10:44:46.360Z","updatedAt":"2019-05-18T10:44:46.360Z"},{"id":"85359a7d-0fc2-4943-9da7-1e5b75b61b46","url":"https://i.imgur.com/baRNKeK.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/baRNKeK.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/baRNKeK.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-05-18T10:44:46.360Z","updatedAt":"2019-05-18T10:44:46.360Z"}],"postAvatar":""}